{"tid":2212254,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"運動抗爭 睇書抗爭 飲水抗爭","createTime":"2020-09-21T15:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T16:21:29.000Z","uid":165234,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc5e1c6e28ef5de1ee72d93b555e17960e1ae116","tid":2212254,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kUWCg6O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUWCg6O.jpg&h=1b1a3e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做下運動 睇下書 飲下水 同抗爭既成敗係有關<br />\n<br />\n可以改變香港 甚至係可以改變整個世界<br />\n<br />\n引用我最鐘意既蝴蝶效應<br />\n<br />\n蝴蝶效應係指初始條件既微小變化 將能帶動整個<br />\n<br />\n系統長期同巨大既連鎖反應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YLwbmBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYLwbmBo.jpg&h=7e08f981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幅圖展示既兩條軌跡（藍色、黃色各一）<br />\n<br />\n兩條軌跡既起點x坐標上只係相差10^-5次方<br />\n<br />\n開始時 兩條軌跡似乎是重合的<br />\n<br />\n但係最終位置表明兩條軌跡 同終點不再重合<br />\n<br />\n換言之 你今日細微既行為 例如推Twitter 食黃店<br />\n<br />\n做Gym 甚至同你既朋友討論政治 <br />\n<br />\n都對12位手足 習近平 特朗普 林鄭 陳彥霖 香港<br />\n<br />\n有舉足輕重嘅影響 呢個影響會係一年 甚至五年後體現"},{"pid":"09ca4b3e7a13d9628dc0d086e389cf865a9481d9","tid":2212254,"uid":165234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"再分享多一樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n2003年既伊拉克戰爭<br />\n<br />\n美軍總共發射咗7200萬粒細口徑既子彈<br />\n<br />\n而當年 訓練所使用既子彈數量係11億粒 <br />\n<br />\n同戰場上所使用既子彈數相差 係15倍<br />\n<br />\n美國陸軍曾經統計過 2002年至2005年其間<br />\n<br />\n一共使用咗60億粒嘅子彈 總共擊殺二萬名既敵軍<br />\n<br />\n而每殺一個敵人 用既子彈數量係30萬粒<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n相反 香港既抗爭者願意投入幾多資源去準備打一場 屬於佢地自己本土 佢哋未來嘅戰爭？</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3fecc00a451ed7eeb2611e425cd583cf93c24a9","tid":2212254,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"please help me do that task<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwitter新戰線: #StopHKCensorship<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2212252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2212252</a>"},{"pid":"db9eba62dfc5d597f9220d65dd7df3859ce21a5f","tid":2212254,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"入到去坐，咪大把時間睇書，操嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗咩咁急"},{"pid":"6340593ea06a7282d037feeda138bd4ed7517579","tid":2212254,"uid":165234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db9eba62dfc5d597f9220d65dd7df3859ce21a5f","tid":2212254,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"入到去坐，咪大把時間睇書，操嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗咩咁急"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"入到去先睇書操嘢 太遲了"},{"pid":"617aecfca6d5251aed85eb54a3877eef2315a950","tid":2212254,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6340593ea06a7282d037feeda138bd4ed7517579","tid":2212254,"uid":165234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db9eba62dfc5d597f9220d65dd7df3859ce21a5f","tid":2212254,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"入到去坐，咪大把時間睇書，操嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗咩咁急"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"入到去先睇書操嘢 太遲了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"但入面都係手足，唱友誼萬歲，同監獄風雲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45dc3dd0c445b3b6233052a1afec4ed75f70e612","tid":2212254,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"我哋面臨嘅係戰爭而唔係抗爭，用抗爭思維去應對戰爭只會得無力感。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2179008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2179008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}